  <h2>About Karooly</h2>
  <p>Dr. Gonzalo Gallardo developed this vocabulary-builder web application as a for-fun <a href="http://rubyonrails.org/" target="_blank">Ruby on Rails</a> project to enhance the materials in his Spanish language classes. Karooly's content consists of self-contained vocabulary lessons, avaialbe from any web browser. After students enroll in a lesson, they go through activities to familiarize with the vocabulary's meaning, spelling and diction.</p><br>

